			<p>Posted in <a href="http://stevenhager420.wordpress.com/category/conspiracy-theory/" rel="category tag">Conspiracy theory</a>, <a href="http://stevenhager420.wordpress.com/category/counterculture-history/" rel="category tag">Counterculture history</a>, <a href="http://stevenhager420.wordpress.com/category/spirituality/" rel="category tag">Spirituality</a></p>
			<p>Tagged with <a href="http://stevenhager420.wordpress.com/tag/angel-dust/" rel="tag">angel dust</a>, <a href="http://stevenhager420.wordpress.com/tag/brian-wilson/" rel="tag">Brian Wilson</a>, <a href="http://stevenhager420.wordpress.com/tag/busy-bee/" rel="tag">Busy Bee</a>, <a href="http://stevenhager420.wordpress.com/tag/coke-la-rock/" rel="tag">Coke La Rock</a>, <a href="http://stevenhager420.wordpress.com/tag/crack-cocaine/" rel="tag">crack cocaine</a>, <a href="http://stevenhager420.wordpress.com/tag/dick-dale/" rel="tag">Dick Dale</a>, <a href="http://stevenhager420.wordpress.com/tag/good-vibrations/" rel="tag">Good Vibrations</a>, <a href="http://stevenhager420.wordpress.com/tag/grandmaster-caz/" rel="tag">Grandmaster Caz</a>, <a href="http://stevenhager420.wordpress.com/tag/hip-hop/" rel="tag">Hip Hop</a>, <a href="http://stevenhager420.wordpress.com/tag/jack-kerouac/" rel="tag">Jack Kerouac</a>, <a href="http://stevenhager420.wordpress.com/tag/lsd/" rel="tag">LSD</a>, <a href="http://stevenhager420.wordpress.com/tag/newport-beach/" rel="tag">Newport Beach</a>, <a href="http://stevenhager420.wordpress.com/tag/religion/" rel="tag">religion</a>, <a href="http://stevenhager420.wordpress.com/tag/society-of-smokers/" rel="tag">Society of Smokers</a>, <a href="http://stevenhager420.wordpress.com/tag/solage/" rel="tag">Solage</a>, <a href="http://stevenhager420.wordpress.com/tag/surfers/" rel="tag">surfers</a></p>		</div>
